#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.77:0.3"
msgid "77. Kalyāṇamittasutta"
msgstr "77. Good Friends"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.36"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.77:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.77:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Nāhaṃ, bhikkhave, aññaṃ ekadhammampi samanupassāmi, yena anuppanno vā ariyo "
"aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo uppajjati, uppanno vā ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo "
"bhāvanāpāripūriṃ gacchati, yathayidaṃ, bhikkhave, kalyāṇamittatā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I do not see a single thing that gives rise to the noble "
"eightfold path, or, if it’s already arisen, develops it to perfection like "
"good friendship."

msgctxt "sn45.77:1.3"
msgid ""
"Kalyāṇamittassetaṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ "
"maggaṃ bhāvessati, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarissati."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with good friends can expect to develop and cultivate the noble "
"eightfold path."

msgctxt "sn45.77:1.4"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, "
"ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant with good friends develop and cultivate the noble "
"eightfold path?"

msgctxt "sn45.77:1.5"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ … pe … "
"sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ "
"vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, "
"right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right "
"immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as "
"letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.77:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, "
"ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarotī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant with good friends develops and cultivates the noble "
"eightfold path.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.77:1.7"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
